name: Nutrisia
tagline: WordPress plugin for Java Multi Mandiri websites.
body:
# Nutrisia: _WordPress plugin for Java Multi Mandiri websites_

Nutrisia is a WordPress plugin to enhance the functionality of Java Multi Mandiri websites,
specificaly WordPress based websites.

Nutrisia is written and crafted for Java Multi Mandiri websites in mind,
so I do warn you that it may be will not able to run smoothly on your site.
But, I try to write this plugin so it can be installed in any general
WordPress-based sites.
note: Don't delete this file! It's used internally to help with page regeneration.
